1
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:12,279
The Empress Dowager has passed away.

2
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:17,000
The Empress made us kneel for six days.

3
00:00:18,079 --> 00:00:20,199
Since she had such deep affection for the Empress Dowager,

4
00:00:20,440 --> 00:00:23,039
the Empress should have been buried with her.

5
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,920
His Majesty arrives!

6
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:48,520
Greetings, Your Majesty.

7
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:54,159
Ruling from behind the curtain for a decade,

8
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,439
the Empress Dowager's dream of ruling

9
00:00:58,359 --> 00:01:00,159
has finally shattered.

10
00:01:06,959 --> 00:01:08,159
Before the Empress Dowager's spirit,

11
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:10,920
Your Majesty must maintain the dignity of a son.

12
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,840
Do not lose your composure.

13
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,519
A son?

14
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:17,359
I served as her puppet for ten years.

15
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,439
Are you not just trying to force me

16
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,280
to allow your aunt

17
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,400
to be buried in the Imperial Mausoleum?

18
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:27,319
What dignity do you speak of to me?

19
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,920
I ask Your Majesty to follow ancestral rules

20
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:35,799
and escort the Empress Dowager's coffin for burial.

21
00:01:40,799 --> 00:01:42,319
And what if I refuse?

22
00:01:50,439 --> 00:01:51,200
Go call the Imperial Physician, quickly!

23
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:51,640
Yes.

24
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,840
I am willing to plead with my life,

25
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:02,400
asking Your Majesty to bury the Empress Dowager in the Imperial Mausoleum.

26
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,680
The Empress Dowager has passed; the Gu clan is fading.

27
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,159
The only one you can rely on now

28
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:08,639
is me.

29
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,879
Will you leave with me,

30
00:02:12,879 --> 00:02:14,280
or do you insist on keeping vigil for the Empress Dowager?

31
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,759
Your Majesty, do not harm your health with anger.

32
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,439
My sister was just anxious for a moment.

33
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:30,159
Since the Empress refuses to leave the mourning hall,

34
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:31,759
let her kneel here to her heart's content.

35
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,560
His Majesty has already left.

36
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,960
Why are you still kneeling?

37
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:41,280
Do you all wish to imitate the Gu clan and defy the Imperial will?

38
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:42,639
Yes, yes.

39
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:51,479
Do you know what this is?

40
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:56,159
This is his love for you.

41
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,960
Empty.

42
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,199
Fake.

43
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:00,439
Illusory.

44
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,800
This one still sits on the Empress's throne.

45
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,800
A mere Noble Concubine

46
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,960
dares to discuss the Emperor and Empress?

47
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,599
Are you not just an abandoned empress in the end?

48
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,159
Are you not skilled at chess?

49
00:03:22,639 --> 00:03:23,520
Now,

50
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,599
how does it feel to be a discarded piece?

51
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:34,759
His Majesty and the Empress

52
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,680
were once a young imperial couple.

53
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,000
Yet in the past two years,

54
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:40,960
due to the Gu clan and the Empress Dowager,

55
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:42,280
they have grown estranged

56
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:43,879
and distant.

57
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,400
Noble Concubine Meng's brother,

58
00:03:46,599 --> 00:03:47,960
for His Majesty in the court,

59
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,439
has purged the Empress Dowager's forces.

60
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:51,479
Now, within the harem,

61
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,960
she is also in the limelight.

62
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:54,680
This harem

63
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,800
is likely about to undergo a great change.

64
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:03,719
Darn it.

65
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,199
Such an ominous sign

66
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,080
portends a great calamity.

67
00:04:13,399 --> 00:04:14,199
Your Majesty.

68
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,160
Please endure a little longer.

69
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:17,959
The Imperial Physician will be here soon.

70
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,120
Your Majesty, what is wrong?

71
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:24,480
Perhaps I am dizzy from kneeling too long.

72
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:26,319
Yinsheng,

73
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:29,000
go pour This one a cup of water.

74
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:30,160
Yes.

75
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,920
Why does This one have no strength left?

76
00:04:47,839 --> 00:04:48,600
Something is wrong.

77
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,319
This scent...

78
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,160
there is something wrong with the incense.

79
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,199
Your Majesty!

80
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,680
Your Majesty the Empress!

81
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,120
Your Majesty!

82
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,079
Fire!

83
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,360
Fire!

84
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:12,560
Someone, help! Save Her Majesty!

85
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,600
Someone come quickly!

86
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,560
Help!

87
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,920
The Empress is still inside!

88
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,720
Hurry!

89
00:05:18,439 --> 00:05:20,160
Is it truly such a great calamity?

90
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,079
How did a fire start so suddenly?

91
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:23,240
The Empress is still inside.

92
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,000
What shall we do?

93
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,759
With such a massive fire,

94
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:26,319
I fear the worst.

95
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:27,120
Buried with the dead.

96
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:30,519
It really was a prophecy fulfilled.

97
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:41,720
This fire is suspicious.

98
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:44,800
In the deep palace, it is hard to tell friend from foe.

99
00:05:45,199 --> 00:05:47,079
Is it an accident or a plot?

100
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:50,240
Is This one truly to perish here?

101
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:51,800
No.

102
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:53,959
Even if the flames consume my body,

103
00:05:54,519 --> 00:05:55,759
I will rise from the ashes.

104
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,639
This one will never accept this fate.

105
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,360
I should be suffering the pain of burning fire.

106
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:19,920
Why is my body so bone-chillingly cold?

107
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,319
Someone, come quickly!

108
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:23,920
Fengqing has fallen into the water!

109
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,399
Someone, help!

110
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,079
This one must survive.

111
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:28,879
Fengqing.

112
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:33,360
Fengqing.

113
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:34,839
Fengqing.

114
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,040
Fengqing.

115
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,319
Come save This one, quickly!

116
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,360
Fengqing.

117
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,720
Fengqing, what is wrong? Fengqing.

118
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:47,079
The 18th day of the second month, Year of Bingwu.

119
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:49,879
The Empress has passed away.

120
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,079
This one...

121
00:06:52,639 --> 00:06:53,600
Passed away?

122
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:01,360
What is this place?

123
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:03,439
Why is This one here?

124
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:06,000
And wearing these clothes...

125
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,480
Fengqing, you are finally awake.

126
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,839
You have been unconscious for three days.

127
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,920
How dare you! Who are you?

128
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,279
Fengqing...

129
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:18,240
What is wrong with you?

130
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:22,360
She calls This one Fengqing.

131
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:38,160
How did This one end up looking like this?

132
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:40,199
Where is this place?

133
00:07:40,639 --> 00:07:41,360
Thi...

134
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:46,040
I have been unconscious for three days?

135
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,800
You must be delirious from falling into the water.

136
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,399
This is the Shangyi Bureau.

137
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,759
Three days ago...

138
00:07:51,759 --> 00:07:54,000
You jumped into the lotus pond in despair.

139
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,600
Why did you try to end your life?

140
00:07:57,279 --> 00:07:58,160
Could it be that...

141
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:01,519
The moment Fengqing drowned herself...

142
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,639
This one took over her body...

143
00:08:04,399 --> 00:08:05,839
And returned from the dead?

144
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:13,000
How could such a bizarre thing happen?

145
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,639
Fortunately, heaven watched over you.

146
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,720
You have no idea what happened...

147
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,040
During these past three days.

148
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,079
The Empress Dowager's mourning hall caught fire.

149
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:25,600
The Empress accidentally perished in the flames.

150
00:08:25,759 --> 00:08:26,560
Accident?

151
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:33,960
No, that was definitely no accident.

152
00:08:33,960 --> 00:08:35,600
I must find a chance to investigate.

153
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,159
So, you are awake.

154
00:08:43,519 --> 00:08:44,919
You certainly have some nerve.

155
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,399
To actually dare to commit suicide.

156
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,360
Wenxin, come here.

157
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,519
Fengqing committed suicide.

158
00:08:52,039 --> 00:08:53,480
She must have been in a desperate situation.

159
00:08:53,519 --> 00:08:55,159
I must tread carefully.

160
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,200
Hurry over to Lanzhi Palace.

161
00:08:57,679 --> 00:09:00,120
Deliver the Silkworm Ceremony dress to Noble Consort Wan.

162
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:00,879
Yes.

163
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,399
Noble Consort Wan?

164
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:03,919
While you were unconscious...

165
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,759
His Majesty has promoted the late Empress's sister...

166
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,919
To the rank of Noble Consort Wan.

167
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:08,559
Do not address your master incorrectly.

168
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,679
Or it could cost you your life.

169
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,279
Yes.

170
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:12,080
Wan'er has been promoted to Noble Consort.

171
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,679
I can take this opportunity to see Wan'er.

172
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,000
Hold this lacquer box carefully.

173
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,279
Or you will be held responsible.

174
00:09:17,279 --> 00:09:17,720
Yes.

175
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,000
Let me go. I...

176
00:09:25,639 --> 00:09:27,120
This slave has rested for three days.

177
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,440
My health is no longer an issue.

178
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,840
I am at the Manager's disposal.

179
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:33,240
That is the first time you have asked for a task.

180
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,279
Very well.

181
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,720
You have an honest nature.

182
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,840
And you are reliable.

183
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,639
Then you shall go.

184
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:39,120
But remember this well.

185
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,120
You must present it to Noble Consort Wan personally.

186
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,679
Do not let anyone else handle it.

187
00:09:43,679 --> 00:09:44,240
Yes.

188
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:51,720
Why did she insist that I not let anyone else handle it?

189
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,120
Could it be...

190
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,600
That there is something wrong with this dress?

191
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,919
Violet pollen.

192
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,200
Wan'er has been allergic to this since childhood.

193
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,360
If it touches her skin...

194
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,480
Her life could be in danger.

195
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:19,639
Who exactly is behind this?

196
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:33,720
Noble Lady De, Concubine Cao, and Lady Su have arrived.

197
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,440
Noble Consort, may you have peace and prosperity.

198
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,320
No need for formalities.

199
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:40,559
Sit down, all of you.

200
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,759
Noble Consort, you are now the head of the concubines.

201
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:49,159
And you are presiding over the Silkworm Ceremony.

202
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,799
It should be a joyous occasion.

203
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:53,639
Why do you still look so sickly?

204
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,080
My elder sister has passed away.

205
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,960
This one has been restless day and night.

206
00:10:57,559 --> 00:10:59,240
It is inevitable to lose one's vitality.

207
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:05,039
I have prepared some blood bird's nest and thousand-year-old ginseng.

208
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:07,039
To nourish Noble Consort Wan's precious body.

209
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:11,120
Now that the Empress's throne is empty.

210
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:13,519
Your Highness will surely enter the Central Palace soon.

211
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:15,200
You must take good care of your health.

212
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:16,960
Su...

213
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,519
Lady Su comes from a merchant family.

214
00:11:18,799 --> 00:11:20,200
Indeed, you are generous.

215
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:23,440
You really are attentive to the Noble Consort.

216
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:26,639
However, the appointment of an Empress...

217
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,080
...is a matter of great importance.

218
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:30,679
Sister, for you to speculate on His Majesty's mind like this...

219
00:11:31,039 --> 00:11:32,799
...what crime should you be charged with?

220
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:34,559
Noble Consort!

221
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,759
I know I was wrong.

222
00:11:35,799 --> 00:11:36,919
I deserve to die ten thousand deaths.

223
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:38,519
As the mistress of Yongfu Palace...

224
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:41,720
...I naturally cannot watch you lose propriety and err.

225
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:52,279
Your Highness, please have some tea.

226
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,399
A slip of the tongue...

227
00:11:59,399 --> 00:12:00,960
...shall be punished on the tongue.

228
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,399
A small punishment to serve as a big warning.

229
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:05,360
To prevent a great disaster in the future.

230
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,039
Concubine Cao...

231
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:08,200
I know I was wrong.

232
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,679
Noble Consort, I beg you...

233
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:11,759
Since Lady Su has knelt and admitted her fault...

234
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,279
...why not let it go?

235
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:15,080
Discussing the Empress's throne in private...

236
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:17,320
...if it reaches His Majesty's ears...

237
00:12:17,799 --> 00:12:19,120
...I fear that even you, Your Highness...

238
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,720
...would be implicated.

239
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:23,919
Sister.

240
00:12:24,879 --> 00:12:26,840
This Cloud Mist Tribute Tea is getting cold.

241
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,519
That wouldn't be good, would it?

242
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:45,480
How dare you!

243
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,559
I know I was wrong!

244
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:47,799
Reporting to Noble Consort.

245
00:12:47,799 --> 00:12:49,679
A maid from the Shangyi Bureau seeks an audience.

246
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:51,759
Perhaps the Shangyi Bureau has brought the ceremonial robe.

247
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:52,879
Send her in.

248
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:03,200
Noble Consort, may you have peace and prosperity.

249
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:12,840
Wan'er has always had a cold constitution.

250
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:15,279
Now her body seems even weaker.

251
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,320
The Silkworm Ceremony is a top priority.

252
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,240
If the ceremonial robe does not fit...

253
00:13:22,519 --> 00:13:24,000
...it will damage the Consort's dignity.

254
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,240
In reply to Your Highness.

255
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:27,000
The Shangyi Bureau worked day and night.

256
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,080
We dare not make any mistake with the ceremonial robe.

257
00:13:29,759 --> 00:13:31,399
Your Highness might as well try it on.

258
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,000
In case there are any oversights...

259
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,600
...we can remedy them in time, can we not?

260
00:13:47,519 --> 00:13:49,360
The style of this ceremonial robe is quite unique.

261
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:51,200
Noble Consort, why not put it on?

262
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:52,600
Let us feast our eyes.

263
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,919
Your Highness, please try it on.

264
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,200
This robe is magnificent.

265
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:58,440
Only Your Highness's grace can match it.

266
00:13:58,759 --> 00:14:01,000
You will surely look radiant in it.

267
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,559
This one has just died...

268
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,759
...and already someone is making a move on Wan'er.

269
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:24,240
The demons and monsters of this harem...

270
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,919
...who exactly is stirring up trouble?
